response.overview: December 18th, 2016 :: Big Japan Pro-Wrestling presents Death Vegas 2016 from the Yokohama Cultural Gymnasium in Yokohama, Kanagawa, Japan with an attendance of 1,981. Matches includes: • Yasufumi Nakanoue & Yuji Okabayashi vs. Kazumi Kikuta & Yoshihisa Uto • Brahman Kei, Brahman Shu, Jaki Numazawa & Tatsuhiko Yoshino vs. Speed Of Sounds (Hercules Senga & Tsutomu Oosugi), Atsushi Maruyama & Shinobu • Table Crash Death Match Masashi Takeda & Takumi Tsukamoto vs. Masaya Takahashi & Takayuki Ueki • Kazuki Hashimoto & Ryuichi Kawakami vs. Daichi Hashimoto & Ryota Hama • Light Tubes Death Match Ryuji Ito & Toshiyuki Sakuda vs. Yankee Two Kenju (Isami Kodaka & Yuko Miyamoto) • Hideki Suzuki & Takuya Nomura vs. Twin Towers (Kohei Sato & Shuji Ishikawa) • BJW World Strong Heavyweight Title Match Hideyoshi Kamitani (c) vs. Daisuke Sekimoto • BJW Death Match Heavyweight Title Light Tubes Double G Shock Death Match Kankuro Hoshino (c) vs. Abdullah Kobayashi.
response.title: BJW Death Vegas 2016
